metadata.description:
HAPPY Valentine's Day!　NECCO_CHAN and OSIRASAMA of binzoko SAN's house are playing a prank on Valentine's Day presents!　They are very cute!    

-----------------------------------    
    
NECCO_CHAN and OSIRASAMA are characters created by binzoko. The characters were created based on her original Hachiware cat, and are now loved by many people in the electronic world.
